[hide param="2.2 (Downloading site content to computer against 2.1)"]<b>When to discipline:</b>&nbsp;In a typical situation, it is hard to determine when someone illegally copies content from our website and saves it to their computer. However, if proof can be obtained of such actions happening, issue this discipline.<br />
<br />
<b>Reason for rule:</b>&nbsp;Downloading content from our website for uses other than permitted is a copyright violation in the eyes of the law.

