<p style="line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in; orphans: 1"><span style="background-color: rgb(186, 186, 255); font-family: monospace; font-weight: bold"><span style="font-family: Open Sans, Segoe UI, Tahoma, Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: #2a212d; "><kbd class="cms_keep_block" title="title">[title param=&quot;2&quot;]Message templates[/title]</kbd><kbd class="cms_keep_block" title="title">[title param=&quot;3&quot;]Description[/title]</kbd> When you warn or punish a user, it is important to include all necessary info within your message to the user in order for them to get the most of it. We have provided a description as well as an example message. We recommend following this format in your discipline messages.</span><br />
<span style="font-family: Open Sans, Segoe UI, Tahoma, Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: #2a212d; ">&mdash;</span><br />
