<p style="orphans: 1"><span style="background-color: rgb(186, 186, 255); font-family: monospace; font-weight: bold"><span style="font-family: Open Sans, Segoe UI, Tahoma, Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: #2a212d; ">If they can appeal the ban, be sure to state so and state the instructions for doing so as described in the rules.<kbd class="cms_keep_block" title="title">[title param=&quot;3&quot;]Example Message[/title]</kbd> Greetings Lovinity.</span><br />
