	<li>
	<p style="margin-bottom: 0in; orphans: 1"><span style="background-color: rgb(186, 186, 255); font-family: monospace; font-weight: bold"><span style="font-family: Open Sans, Segoe UI, Tahoma, Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: #2a212d; ">You have also earned an additional 30-day suspension as a result of the discussion of illegal activity.</span></span></p>
