	<p style="orphans: 1"><span style="background-color: rgb(186, 186, 255); font-family: monospace; font-weight: bold"><span style="font-family: Open Sans, Segoe UI, Tahoma, Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: #2a212d; ">The forum topic containing the illegal activity has been closed and deleted from public eye. However, we will use information from this forum to report the discussion to appropriate authorities.</span></span></p>
